main event: A Methodist minister observed a very large UFO traveling slowly at an estimated altitude of 3000 feet in Fremont, Texas.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for several minutes without an explanation provided., The object was classified as very large and was moving southward., No photographs or physical evidence were associated with the sighting., There was no known air traffic in the area at the time of the sighting., Weather conditions were clear with good visibility during the observation.
